name: Painting Paradise
description: Explore the world of painting with various techniques, from watercolors to acrylics. Campers will create stunning masterpieces and discover their inner artist.

name: Sculpture Sensations
description: Campers will sculpt, mold, and shape their imagination into three-dimensional art. From clay to wire, they'll craft amazing sculptures.

name: Crafty Creations
description: Get ready to dive into the world of crafts! From jewelry making to paper crafting, campers will unleash their creativity through hands-on projects.

name: Art Adventures for Teens
description: Teenagers will explore advanced art techniques, experiment with multimedia, and develop a strong portfolio for future art pursuits.

name: Outdoor Sketching
description: Campers will take their art outdoors to sketch landscapes, animals, and more. This class combines creativity with nature.

name: Pottery Perfection
description: Experience the tactile joy of molding clay into beautiful pottery. Learn various pottery techniques and create functional and decorative pieces.

name: Digital Art Discovery
description: Campers will explore the world of digital art using tablets and software. They'll create digital illustrations, animations, and more.

name: Creative Writing Workshop
description: Nurture the writer within! Campers will explore various writing styles and create their own stories, poems, and more.

name: Mixed Media Magic
description: Blend different art forms like painting, collage, and sculpture to create unique mixed media artworks. Unleash your creativity!

name: Nature Photography
description: Capture the beauty of nature through photography. Campers will learn photography techniques and explore outdoor photo sessions.

name: Drama and Theater Arts
description: Campers will dive into the world of acting, improv, and theater production. They'll stage their own performances and build confidence.

name: Culinary Creations
description: Discover the art of cooking! Campers will learn to prepare delicious dishes and explore culinary creativity in the kitchen.

name: Music Maestros
description: Explore the world of music with instruments, singing, and composition. Campers will create their own musical compositions.

name: Printmaking Explorations
description: Campers will experiment with printmaking techniques such as linocut and etching to create unique and expressive artworks.

name: Textile Arts Adventure
description: Learn the art of textile design, fabric painting, and weaving. Campers will create their own textile masterpieces.

name: Cartooning and Comics
description: Campers will dive into the world of cartooning, character design, and comic book creation. Unleash your inner comic artist!

name: Science and Art Fusion
description: Explore the intersection of art and science! Campers will conduct creative experiments and create artworks inspired by science.

name: Photography Editing
description: Campers will learn photo editing techniques to enhance their photography skills. Dive into the world of digital image manipulation.

name: Exploring Art History
description: Journey through the history of art! Campers will learn about famous artists and create artworks inspired by different art movements.

name: Mosaic Marvels
description: Campers will create stunning mosaic artworks using colorful tiles and glass. Discover the beauty of this ancient art form.
